    Title: I Ching
Title: Peace
---
The government has long been in disarray. Despite all proclamations to the
contrary, ill fortune is at hand. War will only aggravate the situation. The
subject should submit to fate, keep inwardly free, and ameliorate the harm
done to those nearest him. The bad time will pass.
